 the 2026 Event<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a4cceb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0a4cceb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\">Join us for the 55th Annual A Day in the Park Craft Fair on Sunday, July 12, 2026! Over 150 vendors exhibit at this event each year in beautiful Swan Park. Show hours are 9 am to 3 pm.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\">We are now partnering with BoothCentral to streamline our vendor application process.<br \/><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\">New to BoothCentral? First register at by clicking the button above or go to: <a href=\"https:\/\/my.boothcentral.com\/v\/events\/a-day-in-the-park-craft-fair-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/my.boothcentral.com\/v\/events\/a-day-in-the-park-craft-fair<\/a><\/span><\/p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\">Then, fill out all required fields in the Contact Information section and press &#8220;Save.&#8221; BoothCentral will automatically fill in all of your saved information to save you time.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\">Booths\u00a0are\u00a0$80\u00a0each (sorry, no refunds). Each booth is 10 ft x 10 ft. Vendors need to provide their own tables and chairs. We also recommend a canopy as the event is held rain or shine. You can start setting up at 6:00 am. We have volunteers on hand to help you get your items to your booth. These same volunteers will help you load leftover product to your vehicle at the end of the show. Booths must stay up until 3 pm.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\">Questions: Email <a href=\"mailto:kathleengittus619@gmail.com\">kathleengittus619@gmail.com<\/a>.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2b97507 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2b97507\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7673973\" data-id=\"7673973\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c0e6c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"4c0e6c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1178\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2764\" alt=\"Group of people at Art event looking at local artists art work\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-scaled.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-300x184.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-1024x628.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-768x471.jpg 768w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-1536x942.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-2048x1256.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ArtInThePark-600x368.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-fa09888 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"fa09888\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-70cfba2\" data-id=\"70cfba2\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c81eda8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c81eda8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Women\u2019s Affiliate of Beaver Dam Area<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31766b1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"31766b1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Mission<\/strong><br \/>Organized in 1962, The Women&#8217;s Affiliate of the Beaver Dam Area Chamber and Visitor Center is dedicated to the beautification of Beaver Dam and the promotion of business and goodwill within our community. Now as the Women&#8217;s Affiliate of the Beaver Dam Area,\u00a0the membership continues in the spirit of goodwill and positive contributions to the Beaver Dam Community. For contact information include an email address: <a href=\"womensaffiliate@gmail.com\">womensaffiliate@gmail.com<\/a><\/span><\/p><p><b>Our History<br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Women&#8217;s Affiliate of the Chamber of Commerce was formed in 1962 at a time in history when women were not accepted as members of the Chamber of Commerce. The Charter members represented a cross section of our community and a variety of entrepreneurial occupations. These women had a desire to make a contribution and to work positively for Beaver Dam. The initial name of the group was the &#8220;Chambermaids&#8221; and reflected the sense of humor, and spirit of fun, that the initial group possessed. Now as the &#8220;Women&#8217;s Affiliate&#8221; the membership continues in the spirit of good will and positive contributions to the Beaver Dam Community.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-61a7d01 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"61a7d01\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-603af59\" data-id=\"603af59\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3aee94d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3aee94d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Membership<br \/><\/b>Any person who supports the objectives of the Chamber and is actively engaged in, or retired from, business, industry, government, public services or the professions is welcome to join.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-aa04f15\" data-id=\"aa04f15\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc86cb3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bc86cb3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Dues<br \/><\/b>There are no dues to be a member of the Women&#8217;s Affiliate of the Beaver Dam Area<\/p><p><b>Meetings<br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Meetings are held the second Wednesday of each month, usually at Tower Lanes.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4e33630\" data-id=\"4e33630\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff70c2e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ff70c2e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Contact Us<br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more information and\/or a membership application:<\/span><\/p><p><b>Women&#8217;s Affiliate<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PO Box 95<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Beaver Dam, WI 53916<br \/><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; color: #080808;\"><a href=\"mailto:womensaffiliate@gmail.com\">womensaffiliate@gmail.com<\/a><\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-23803a0 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"23803a0\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b5bb14a\" data-id=\"b5bb14a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b025a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"9b025a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d76ff9e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d76ff9e\" data-element_type